{"tid":997801,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"冰島tour 問題","createTime":"2019-01-27T12:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T09:27:59.000Z","uid":40542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f1ade1d7401f727702bee7f69f0e633c8bd4a2","tid":997801,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟3月去，base 係Rejyakvik，無車牌<br />\n之前book咗個係會去south coast 但唔包glacier walk<br />\n<br />\n但宜家又想book 個glacier walk / ice caving 嘅tour，<br />\n但search完發覺由Rejyakvik出發去Skafatell 嘅glacier walk tour 都係會重覆返之前south coast tour 個堆景點 (Seljalandsfoss Waterfall, Sk&oacute;gafoss Waterfall, Black Sand Beach）<br />\n<br />\n想問下如果想book glacier walk tour 除咗硬食個重復south coast景點嘅tour 之外，<br />\n係咪無辦法了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f26d57ed3d6e52710ec2daa7549a17e8b7d59b","tid":997801,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45810fb3d81c947b83d5d2ccba510666c9a844d7","tid":997801,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"大把直去glacier 既TOUR.<br />\n你搵day  tour 個D崶係"},{"pid":"1830c7fe72bc72d04b9fa4f47c420d7f46580b0e","tid":997801,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45810fb3d81c947b83d5d2ccba510666c9a844d7","tid":997801,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"大把直去glacier 既TOUR.<br />\n你搵day  tour 個D崶係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:43:11.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我搵咗10個tour<br />\n都係會經個兩個waterfall<br />\n想請問有無啲係真係直去唔會停低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a5b02e5ef6c6cde9ecc7da0605f1c7afdd843a","tid":997801,"uid":138226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:50:33.000Z","msg":"重覆地方其實無問題<br />\n個2個waterfall 其實得半個鐘 or less 時間比你睇<br />\n<br />\n睇2次都唔太夠"},{"pid":"138ce2ee621ab8c84f5affd079305ee26f6c8534","tid":997801,"uid":11611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:53:21.000Z","msg":"ice cave tour book 2日1夜 tour 會好d, 因為離reykjavik 幾遠下 , 即日來回坐車坐到你暈"},{"pid":"550c3e66ecc55512a2c28d9c3684ef033698dfcc","tid":997801,"uid":39816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"咁睇返你之前book個唔包glacier walk既south coast有無得取消, 有既就唔使煩<br />\n我之前book個tour係可以24小時前免費取消<br />\n唔得既咪睇多次waterfall啦, 去iceland一定要去glacier walk"},{"pid":"10bbf7bbf72354f33e6d7398389d14eacc5ff9c2","tid":997801,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:46:14.000Z","msg":"有直接行冰川的tour.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">乜tour 都勢係假，一定要揀無中文翻譯的tour. 唔係包你後悔<br />\n<br />\n利申我果次個tour 1帶4，另一對英國夫婦</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea3d0776a7d574c80daa546b4d91ddfcd440e9c8","tid":997801,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"唔該曬咁多位巴打~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後揀咗Langj&ouml;kull Glacier <br />\n咁就唔使同south coast 行程撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e8086f8402438cafcbbc6f44f0a5b2db98d85b","tid":997801,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10bbf7bbf72354f33e6d7398389d14eacc5ff9c2","tid":997801,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":